patthana16.23:2.1_0: Kusalaṁ bāhiraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nabāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana16.23:3.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate nava.
patthana16.23:4.1_0: Abyākataṁ upādā dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo naupādā dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.23:5.1_0: Kusalaṁ noupādā dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo nanoupādā dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana16.23:5.1_2: adhipatiyā pannarasa …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate pannarasa.
patthana16.23:6.1_0: Abyākataṁ upādinnaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo naupādinno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.23:6.1_1: Abyākataṁ upādinnaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo naupādinno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.23:6.1_2: Abyākataṁ upādinnaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo naupādinno ca naakusalo naupādinno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
